# Private Groups & Itineraries Implementation Plan

This document outlines the architecture, data flow, and step-by-step roadmap for upgrading Udaipur Scrollbook from a global journal into a **Private Trip Planner & Collaborative Journal**.

## 1. Architectural Changes (Database)

We will introduce a new core model to MongoDB called `Trip`. We will also upgrade our `Photo` model to be "Trip-Aware".

### New Model: `Trip`
This acts as the vault for a private group and holds the master schedule.
*   **`name`**: e.g., "Monsoon Getaway 2026"
*   **`adminId`**: Reference to the User who created it.
*   **`members`**: Array of User IDs who have joined. The ultimate privacy gate lock.
*   **`inviteCode`**: A randomly generated unique 6-character code (e.g., `XJ9K2L`) to easily share on WhatsApp.
*   **`itinerary`**: An array of objects defining the chosen places and their order.
    *   `placeSlug`, `placeName`, `order` (number), `plannedDate` (optional).

### Updated Model: `Photo`
*   **`tripId`**: (NEW) Reference to the specific Trip this photo belongs to.
*   *Cloudinary Path update*: We will dynamically change the upload folder from `scrollbook/{placeSlug}` to `scrollbook/trips/{tripId}/{placeSlug}` to keep Cloudinary organized per group.

---

## 2. API Flow & Backend Roadmap

We will create a new set of API routes to handle the Trip logic securely.

*   **`POST /api/trips`**: Creates a new trip, sets the creator as Admin, generates an invite code.
*   **`POST /api/trips/join`**: Accepts an `inviteCode`. If valid, adds the logged-in User to the `members` array.
*   **`GET /api/trips`**: Fetches all trips where the user is a member (to populate their homepage).
*   **`PUT /api/trips/:id/itinerary`**: Accepts a new array of places. Only the Admin (or authorized members) can save the re-ordered list.
*   **`GET /api/trips/:id/photos`**: Retrieves photos. The server explicitly checks if the requester is in the `members` array before returning a single image.
*   **`POST /api/trips/:id/photos`**: Securely uploads a photo specifically into this private trip vault.

